==English==

===Etymology===
From Dutch ''tafereel'', a panel, picture,  diminutive of ''tafel'', table. Dutch from the Latin ''tabula'', table.

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

#{{nautical}} the [[railing]] around the [[stern]] of a [[ship]]
#{{nautical}} the flat, upper part of a ship's stern

